author: @parvatinair4233
text:
There are times when idol-fan relationships are misunderstood, especially in the context of K-pop. Many people judge or mock those who find joy and comfort in supporting idols, often questioning how someone can find happiness in individuals who are distant, unaware of their existence. I have personally experienced this, as someone close to me once dismissed my happiness in such a relationship. But I smiled through it because I understood the depth and fulfillment that this bond brings.

In difficult times, when nothing else seemed to help, I found solace in TWICE and their music, especially through "TWICE Time to TWICE" (TTT). Their genuine smiles and the covers they release show me that they do care, even from afar. Among all the members, Dahyun holds a special place in my heart. She stands out in a unique way, and her covers are particularly healing. The way she sings has the power to bring comfort, if not complete healing, then at least a momentary sense of peace.

I wish her nothing but happiness, health, and every blessing life has to offer. May success and joy surround her, always, as she has done for so many. For in her light, many of us have found our own.
